item.title: [REPLAY] The Father Effect | CP119
item.description: In today's episode, we are shining the spotlight on Fatherhood and all the unique strengths and challenges that come with being a dad. With various external factors impacting our children and parenting as a whole, it's crucial to explore the role of fathers.Join me for this week's episode, let's gain insights and perspectives on how to navigate fatherhood in these extraordinary times... item.title: Gabrielle Union
item.description: This week, Kevin Harts sits down with actor, businesswoman, and friend Gabrielle Union. They discuss Gab's legendary acting career and business ventures and give us a behind-the-scenes look at their friendship. Keep an eye out for her upcoming Netflix romantic comedy, The Perfect Find, and her BET Plus special, Gabrielle Union: My Journey to 50. Feed: https://feeds.simplecast.com/ijknOKeU
